{"tid":695423,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"遇上食素嘅橫蠻無野客人","createTime":"2018-06-09T07:24:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-09T07:51:42.000Z","uid":136499,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"62de4720fa0bf2682144d4a50b2e5864c76595a0","tid":695423,"uid":136499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T07:24:30.000Z","msg":"頭先飲茶有兩公婆屌鳩啲侍應<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :兩公婆  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :侍應<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 喂我嗌鼓油王炒麵點解會有肉? 我食素架<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 我地嘅鼓油王炒麵係有肉架，不過我整多個比你啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 我嗌鼓油王炒麵就係咁簡單，點解會有肉?<br />\n<br />\n然後個廚師出黎，有啲嬲咁收走<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 自己做錯仲發脾氣。我同你講呀唔好就咁揀走啲肉就算，再整過呀!<br />\n<br />\n問題係原來兩公婆落單根本冇話走肉，只係自己天真以為冇肉，仲聲大夾惡屌人。唔知佢地因為乜原因食素，但如果為左食素浪費一大碟麵，我諗真係有啲反智。"},{"pid":"3150063ca11302905a9a36dcd36dd20900e64a4d","tid":695423,"uid":136499,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T07:25:52.000Z","msg":"對唔住打錯係橫蠻無理先啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3ce29327e8a0d3c9f155ca640b56f62c552860c","tid":695423,"uid":131686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T07:27:12.000Z","msg":"on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e97232c78455c1b94ec161816126fbb208c4f133","tid":695423,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T07:27:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b0606a3e04a2789a71ec4edba425356d677d945c","tid":695423,"uid":16511,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T07:28:53.000Z","msg":"我剩係食肉嫁 , <br />\n<br />\n點解d 麵唔係用肉做嫁"},{"pid":"b2d18871c61107334933fece6de6133d3577a663","tid":695423,"uid":14014,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T07:28:57.000Z","msg":"香港不嬲多西客"},{"pid":"4b19bb4265994f3afd81c8c6ad0b5ca0873b65fd","tid":695423,"uid":16230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e97232c78455c1b94ec161816126fbb208c4f133","tid":695423,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T07:27:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T07:29:27.000Z","msg":"屌你老母你死未"},{"pid":"1dcfcd04a37e2ccd2a8eb1a0fffdfba28174de84","tid":695423,"uid":77712,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T07:30:03.000Z","msg":"你估個廚師再炒出來的，只係會走肉的豉油王炒麵咁簡單咩，對付d西客要有耐性去做出最好的食物給西客品嚐的"},{"pid":"215838e755c70bf3eb7e381e3bdc33af790491fe","tid":695423,"uid":92619,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T07:38:59.000Z","msg":"我自己都食素，但去非素食餐廳一定會問清楚<br />\n人地本身都唔係做素食，自己問多聲又無死<br />\n無問到就係自己唔小心<br />\n非素食餐廳肯做走肉已經好好，況且如果道菜真係無得走肉，咪叫第二款<br />\n除非佢寫係素食之選，但係入面有肉姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5e298606f899d0be8449be141e57869e5afc8fa","tid":695423,"uid":136499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T07:42:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我自己都食素，但去非素食餐廳一定會問清楚<br />\n人地本身都唔係做素食，自己問多聲又無死<br />\n無問到就係自己唔小心<br />\n非素食餐廳肯做走肉已經好好，況且如果道菜真係無得走肉，咪叫第二款<br />\n除非佢寫係素食之選，但係入面有肉姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講得啱，我覺得食素食肉係個人選擇無得屌，但如果因為自己嘅選擇麻煩到人就好有問題，理撚得你食乜。"},{"pid":"0cbc2d9db1c599cef8e3972897dac1026efd2f16","tid":695423,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T07:44:08.000Z","msg":"鼓"},{"pid":"104f9fef26368b82e732854ab60d8b4ca93f9cd8","tid":695423,"uid":81598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T07:51:42.000Z","msg":"做客既最唔得罪得既就係侍應同廚師，<br />\n一陣加d口水鼻涕鼻屎落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}